  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/kernel\/iofilterscheme\/1811248-synchronizecache\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T21:45:59Z\n---\n\n# synchronizeCache\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvirtual IOReturn synchronizeCache(\n IOService *client); \n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- **client**: Client requesting the cache synchronization.\n\n## Return Value\n\nReturns the status of the cache synchronization.\n\n## Overview\n\nFlush the cached data in the storage object, if any, synchronously.\n\n## Miscellaneous\n\n- **copyPhysicalExtent**\n- **handleClose**\n- **handleIsOpen**\n- **handleOpen**\n- **lockPhysicalExtents**\n- **read**\n- **unlockPhysicalExtents**\n- **unmap**\n- **write**\n\n",
